{"tid":708043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"環保殺，回收父母系列","createTime":"2018-06-19T05:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T09:23:08.000Z","uid":191338,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f99525f49ee1f5c5c7ab819547b7a9bc0e93ccb","tid":708043,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n構成環保殺需要嘅因素:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔嘅教唆 - 正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鑽牛角尖嘅仔女/仆街嘅父母 - 負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n濕疹困擾 23歲女弒父母自殺<br />\n剛大學護理學院畢業 涉父親節行兇<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180619/s00001/1529346031352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180619%2Fs00001%2F1529346031352&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=878e8eb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180619%2Fs00001%2F1529346031352&h=88edbee4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180619/s00001/1529346031352</a><br />\n<br />\n弒母案疑兇患抑鬱 曾說「你死咗我就會跟住死」<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171010/mobile/odn-20171010-1010_00176_009.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171010%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20171010-1010_00176_009.html&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=cbbe41ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20171010/mobile/odn-20171010-1010_00176_009.html</a><br />\n<br />\n喪男殺爸媽　雪櫃藏人頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130316/18197429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130316%2F18197429&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0282e05a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130316%2F18197429&h=10fae75f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130316/18197429</a><br />\n殺父母罪成判囚終身<br />\n周凱亮聞拍檔脫罪爆粗<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150324/19087832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150324%2F19087832&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=650854a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150324%2F19087832&h=0243d1ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150324/19087832</a><br />\n<br />\n逆子弒親 父死母危<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130317/mobile/odn-20130317-0317_00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20130317%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20130317-0317_00174_001.html&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=db6808aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130317/mobile/odn-20130317-0317_00174_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n品味蘋果：港式弒親<br />\n張經緯眼中的倫常崩壞<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180121&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20280827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180121%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20280827&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=737dec92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180121%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20280827&h=ba99a874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180121&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20280827</a><br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆，如果好似外國咁大地方<br />\n仔女搬晒出去住有咩可能會做到環保殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbetween, 有幾多人認識精神暴力同精神虐殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462a1317a2e3b7698d379fc8b74533497c2d2776","tid":708043,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:20:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d42dbdbc7e5c6cf7478404a612fb8df3b18de717","tid":708043,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"回收廢物、轉用慳電膽等是不少人常用的環保措施，但瑞典一項研究發現，要大幅減少碳排放保護環境，最「有效」的方法就是不生小朋友，有團體就鼓勵節育，認為「兩個就夠晒數」。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典隆德大學（Lund University）研究指，住在發達國家的人如果不生小朋友的話，平均每年可額外減少58.6噸碳排放，比任何節約措施帶來的影響更大，但研究發現西方國家雖然會鼓勵民眾回收廢物保護環境，卻沒有一個提倡節育。<br />\n<br />\n香港更進一步，領先全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e816a7448eebbaab86e794b762baf2d4cbf6c94","tid":708043,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"一定係周凱亮最巔 佢以為自己係奇拿咁"},{"pid":"0738335b5369a0ab79cb7755d8e1e0028e04ccbe","tid":708043,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:23:08.000Z","msg":"元朗劍客都唔弱"}]}